# Slash Commands

This folder is for custom commands and scripts to process your work notes.

## Purpose
Store automation scripts, processing tools, and custom commands here.

## Examples
- `process_notes.py` - Python script to parse work notes
- `generate_summaries.sh` - Shell script to create all output formats
- `sync_to_jira.js` - Node.js script to sync with project management tools

## Usage
Add your custom scripts here and document them in the main README.